Description Annotate an image.
Annotating an image gives the ability to add extra context on your already existing images.
Command codefresh annotate image &lt;id&gt;
Aliases codefresh annotate img &lt;id&gt;
Arguments    Option Alias Default Description     id   Docker image full name or id    Options    Option Alias Default Description     --help   Print help information   --label -l  annotations to add to the image    Examples Annotate an image with a single label codefresh annotate image 2dfacdaad466 -l coverage=75%

